item.title: EAT, DRINK and CONNECT
item.description:
Time: 7PM - 9PM

Date: April 20

Location: 7/F, Club 7, Universal House (near the Elizabeth House), 230 Gloucester Road, Wanchai

The International Entrepreneur Institute in collaboration with the China-Phillipines-Hong-Kong Business Exchange Association invites you to its first event.

Join us for an evening of happy hour, music and fun.

Register now Contact Us
